### Unified Checkout API Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000/api/v1/unified-checkout
### Requires authentication with JWT token

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4080/api/v1
@authUrl = http://localhost:4080/api/v1/auth/email/login

### ============================================================================
### AUTHENTICATION
### ============================================================================

### Login as admin user
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{authUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@cody.inc",
  "password": "password"
}

### Store token from login response
@token = {{loginAdmin.response.body.token}}

### ============================================================================
### UNIFIED CHECKOUT ENDPOINTS
### ============================================================================

### Get Unified Checkout Preview
### Returns preview of all selected cart items (products + services)
### with pricing, availability, and combined totals
# @name getUnifiedPreview
GET {{baseUrl}}/unified-checkout/preview
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Unified Checkout Preview with addresses
### Pass delivery and service address IDs for shipping calculation
# @name getUnifiedPreviewWithAddresses
GET {{baseUrl}}/unified-checkout/preview?delivery_address_id=1&service_address_id=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Unified Checkout Preview with shipping method
# @name getUnifiedPreviewWithShipping
GET {{baseUrl}}/unified-checkout/preview?delivery_address_id=1&shipping_method_id=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### ============================================================================
### PROCESS CHECKOUT
### ============================================================================

### Process Unified Checkout (basic - no addresses specified)
### Creates checkout order + sales order (if products) + bookings (if services)
# @name processCheckoutBasic
POST {{baseUrl}}/unified-checkout/process
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Process Unified Checkout (with delivery address for products)
# @name processCheckoutWithDelivery
POST {{baseUrl}}/unified-checkout/process
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "delivery_address_id": 1,
  "notes": "Please call before delivery"
}

### Process Unified Checkout (with service address for services)
# @name processCheckoutWithService
POST {{baseUrl}}/unified-checkout/process
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "service_address_id": 1,
  "notes": "Gate code: 1234"
}

### Process Unified Checkout (full - products + services)
# @name processCheckoutFull
POST {{baseUrl}}/unified-checkout/process
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "delivery_address_id": 1,
  "service_address_id": 1,
  "shipping_method_id": 1,
  "payment_method": "dragonpay",
  "notes": "Combined order - products and services",
  "idempotency_key": "{{$uuid}}"
}

### ============================================================================
### TEST SCENARIOS
### ============================================================================

### Test 1: Empty cart checkout (should fail)
### First clear cart or use account with empty cart
# @name testEmptyCart
GET {{baseUrl}}/unified-checkout/preview
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Test 2: Checkout with only products
### Add products to cart first, then call preview/process

### Test 3: Checkout with only services
### Add services to cart first, then call preview/process

### Test 4: Checkout with mixed cart (products + services)
### Add both products and services to cart, then call preview/process

### ============================================================================
### HELPER ENDPOINTS (for testing)
### ============================================================================

### Get current user's cart
# @name getMyCart
GET {{baseUrl}}/shopping-carts/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Add product to cart (example)
# @name addProductToCart
POST {{baseUrl}}/shopping-carts/1/items
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "variant_id": 1,
  "quantity": 1,
  "is_selected": true
}

### Add service to cart (example)
# @name addServiceToCart
POST {{baseUrl}}/shopping-carts/1/services
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "service_id": 1,
  "scheduled_date": "2026-02-01",
  "scheduled_start_time": "09:00:00",
  "quantity": 1,
  "is_selected": true
}

